    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for a Class II device at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate that CFD predictions of NIH and RH index are sufficiently accurate to support the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five operating points. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission at the Medium assurance level.",
